OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will be dry with
OL,6,Fsome hazy sunshine. Then high cloud
OL,7,Fwill thicken through the afternoon to
OL,8,Fbring the odd light shower, but with
OL,9,Fstill plenty of dry weather. Light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLargely dry with some late
OL,13,Fevening brightness at first, before
OL,14,Flow cloud gradually spreads south
OL,15,Fthrough the evening and overnight
OL,16,Fbringing some patchy light rain or
OL,17,Fdrizzle at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
