OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FIt will be a largely cloudy
OL,6,Fmorning with some outbreaks of light
OL,7,Frain and drizzle. Drier through the
OL,8,Fafternoon with some brighter spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Freshening northeast
OL,10,Fwinds. Feeling cooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCool
OL,13,Fand quite cloudy on Sunday, but some
OL,14,Fbright spells at times. Early rain on
OL,15,FMonday followed by showers continuing
OL,16,Fthrough Tuesday, these heavy and
OL,17,Fblustery at times. Turning colder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
